    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原子突袭》是一款 3D 街机射击游戏，每隔 2-3 个地点就会出现令人难以置信的动态变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >叙述</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类的技术飞跃并没有被外界忽视。在城市的中央，传送门打开了，成群结队的无情生物从那里涌入，它们只想做一件事--毁灭人类。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了阻止入侵，人们不得不动用核武库，向自己的城市发射导弹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个人都以为这样就足够了，但如果传送门被破坏，残余的外星人就会设法适应，建立移动实验室，用生物质和金属制造新的 “士兵”，目的只有一个--毁灭人类。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人难以置信的高动态</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您目前所看到的一切都爬行在...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196730/extras/9e652544f44fbf3b4add98d4ef08bef1.avif?t=1765878299\" width=243 height=239 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为英雄和武器提供大量缓冲/削弱效果</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心选择，因为每种奖励都会改变一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196730/extras/836e32e2300c2fa84f223d3351abc621.poster.avif?t=1765878299\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196730/extras/836e32e2300c2fa84f223d3351abc621.webm?t=1765878299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196730/extras/836e32e2300c2fa84f223d3351abc621.mp4?t=1765878299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“小心 &quot;操作员凯特 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她的讽刺比怜悯更强烈，所以不要把她的话放在心上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196730/extras/b784d7b8f2c3b00c3d2d50ba07189d39.avif?t=1765878299\" width=306 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在线排行榜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解自己的实力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196730/extras/f7367744aa9f9139feb94961393294d2.poster.avif?t=1765878299\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196730/extras/f7367744aa9f9139feb94961393294d2.webm?t=1765878299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196730/extras/f7367744aa9f9139feb94961393294d2.mp4?t=1765878299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏过程中的玩法变化</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时刻准备迎接新事物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196730/extras/a282625858c509f03f3d69ce9dd35b18.poster.avif?t=1765878299\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196730/extras/a282625858c509f03f3d69ce9dd35b18.webm?t=1765878299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196730/extras/a282625858c509f03f3d69ce9dd35b18.mp4?t=1765878299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来系好安全带。游戏中会有大量敌人、速度和乐趣。</p>",
